306
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:05,670
Yes.

307
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,870
You trust me that much?

308
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:10,600
I've always

309
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,840
followed your lead.

310
