315
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,630
Hello?

316
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:28,270
It's me.

317
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:29,960
Okay.

318
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,200
Thanks.

319
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,440
