320
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,200
Hongtu Trading.

321
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:38,550
Assistant to the president.

322
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,960
Fang Wanzhi,

323
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,200
