328
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:48,080
No one could resist your smile.

329
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:48,910
Li Juan,

330
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:49,630
since when

331
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:51,080
