332
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:53,670
I was not kidding!
I was telling the truth!

333
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,440
Gosh, if that's true,

334
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,030
and they hired you,

335
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,600
