336
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,790
Little Friend,

337
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:07,480
eat more!

338
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:08,200
Wanzhi

339
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,750
is gonna work for a big company!

340
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:13,960
From now on,

341
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:14,670
