345
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:24,600
President Yan's regular restaurants.

346
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,510
Check them out.

347
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:27,910
These are

348
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:29,240
our key clients.

349
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,720
You can get in touch with them

350
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,150
and introduce yourself.

351
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,000
Okay.

352
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,600
For higher level clients,

353
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:36,790
such as those President Yan
contacts directly,

354
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,150
don't ask for cards.

355
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,480
When they're talking

356
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,550
or having a meal,

357
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,000
provide good service,

358
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:42,960
then step aside.

359
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,750
You might

360
00:15:44,870 --> 00:15:45,870
