366
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:55,000
Leaking trade secrets intentionally

367
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,600
carries legal consequences.

368
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:57,840
Got it.

369
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,790
At work, call him President Yan.

370
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,480
After work, Mr. Yan.

371
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:03,360
Avoid disturbing him after hours.

372
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,360
He doesn't like taking calls.

373
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:06,840
But if it's urgent,

374
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,960
