381
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:17,080
Don't ask about his personal affairs.

382
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:19,510
No curiosity. No meddling.

383
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:20,600
Yes.

384
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:22,510
Enjoy your work.

385
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,440
Thanks, Ms. Yao.

386
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:09,880
(Come in.)

387
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,070
President Yan,

388
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:14,440
