I only drink water.

392
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:25,680
I'll be out here.

393
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,920
Call me if you need anything.

394
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,310
Tell the driver

395
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,480
