Okay.

405
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:45,440
Room 8888, for three people.

406
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:46,640
You go order.

407
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,440
Yes.

408
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,680
Any preferences?

409
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:53,200
Yao Qianyun

410
