420
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,550
Mr. Huo, President Yan is out.

421
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:23,550
Bring the car around.

422
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:25,640
I'll get a case

423
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:26,960
