424
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:28,200
You're too kind.

425
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,200
Don't call me Mr. Yan.

426
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:34,000
Just call me Yan.

427
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,270
Your car is here.

428
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:35,920
Please.

429
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:36,720
Take care!

430
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,960
Please help me out with the project.

431
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,240
