433
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:47,110
Sure.

434
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,110
I'm good.

435
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:49,830
I got it.

436
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:51,110
Alright, I'm off.

437
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:58,920
Tell HR

438
00:19:59,070 --> 00:19:59,720
