474
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,880
It's on a tight schedule.

475
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:37,830
Overtime pays double.

476
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:39,070
I asked the manager

477
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,270
