478
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:42,240
You already work long hours.

479
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:43,400
You're young.

480
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,510
Don't wear yourself out.

481
00:21:44,790 --> 00:21:45,720
Don't worry, Auntie.

482
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:46,640
I'm fine.

483
00:21:47,030 --> 00:21:48,880
Instead of working,
I'm afraid of no work.

484
00:21:54,590 --> 00:21:55,110
President Yan.

485
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:59,240
We've gone from 18 microns down to 13

486
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,830
