487
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:03,110
and we've always been working

488
00:22:03,110 --> 00:22:04,400
with the same agent.

489
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:06,110
I hope this year we can ramp up

490
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:08,790
our efforts in technology.

491
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,030
(Come in.)

492
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,590
Great working with you.

493
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,590
Likewise.

494
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,720
Take care, Mr. Yan.

495
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:28,310
Bye.

496
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,160
Bye.

497
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:31,640
Please.

498
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:35,960
Next time you're in Shenzhen,

499
00:22:36,110 --> 00:22:37,310
