500
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,070
Sure.

501
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:39,480
Well, see you.

502
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,240
Thank you.

503
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,000
See you.

504
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,030
President Yan.

505
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:53,350
Nice work today.

506
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:55,240
Go home and rest up.

507
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,880
President Yan.

508
