509
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:46,590
Come in.

510
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:50,680
President Yan, all fixed.

511
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:53,960
Sorry.

512
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:56,400
