516
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,590
I don't have any plans tonight.

517
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,350
You're free to go.

518
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,590
Whoever becomes President Yan's wife

519
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,550
