520
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:22,920
He's so picky.

521
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:24,480
Forget the company.

522
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,350
I doubt there's any woman in Shenzhen

523
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,960
