524
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,310
Here we go.

525
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,160
What's for dinner?

526
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,350
Hot pot?

527
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,030
Sure.

528
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,680
There's a great one near the company.

529
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:36,200
Dying for it.

530
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,400
You're back so early.

531
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:43,640
That's rare.

532
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:45,880
Seriously, rare.

533
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:52,790
Hungry?

534
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:54,790
I'll make you hot pot.

535
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,270
Good.

536
00:24:57,110 --> 00:24:58,240
Juan, thank you.

537
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,350
I'm gonna take a nap.

538
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,720
Alright, get some rest.

539
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:01,920
I'll go get some stuff.

540
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:23,480
Hi, Ms. Yao.

541
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:24,550
Ms. Fang,

542
00:25:24,830 --> 00:25:25,590
I just sent you

543
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:26,240
