544
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,310
Urgent signature needed.

545
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,960
So, find President Yan

546
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,440
(and get the signed document)

547
00:25:30,510 --> 00:25:31,480
(to me)

548
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:32,240
(by 11 PM.)

549
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:32,790
(I'll)

550
00:25:32,830 --> 00:25:34,030
(be waiting at Luohu Port.)

551
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,240
I'll do it right away.

552
00:26:58,110 --> 00:26:58,720
Hi, lady.

553
00:26:58,830 --> 00:26:59,880
What can I do for you?

554
