557
00:27:05,590 --> 00:27:06,000
No.

558
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:07,720
Don't disturb him.

559
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:09,550
There's a lounge.

560
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,640
You can sit and rest.

561
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:11,790
Want something to drink?

562
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:13,030
