563
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:14,350
Drinks are complimentary.

564
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:15,350
Thanks.

565
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:16,790
I'm fine waiting here.

566
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:17,960
Fine.

567
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,790
Just call me if you need anything.

568
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:51,720
Sorry,

569
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,720
President Yan.

570
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:54,480
Need your signature on this.

571
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,160
Yao Qianyun

572
