573
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:06,160
Did you get here early?

574
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,270
It's okay.

575
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:08,880
Only waited a little while.

576
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,640
Why didn't you call me?

577
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:12,200
If time allows,

578
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:12,920
I respect

579
00:28:13,030 --> 00:28:14,160
