580
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:16,310
This is your personal time too,

581
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:17,880
but you're working.

582
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,790
I'm your assistant.

583
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,000
I get paid more

584
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:22,920
than regular staff.

585
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,000
That means

586
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,270
being on call

587
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,240
during personal time when needed.

588
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,350
I'm off now.

589
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:31,350
Yeah.

590
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:51,880
(Ms. Yao!)

591
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:53,920
(Ms. Yao!)

592
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,790
Cutting it close, huh?

593
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:57,270
If I don't go now, I'll be too late.

594
00:28:57,830 --> 00:28:58,640
Great.

595
00:28:58,880 --> 00:28:59,640
Just in time.

596
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,830
Another trip for you.

597
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,720
This is for President Yan
from the Chairman.

598
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,920
Get it there tonight.

