Tong Fan can't be held liable.

899
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,760
(He already accepted)

900
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,000
(the offer from Yinshidai.)

901
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,840
(He stayed behind)

902
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,030
(just to act)

903
00:42:08,030 --> 00:42:09,280
(as their mole.)

904
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:10,840
Our board meeting

905
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,400
was held on a cruise ship

906
00:42:13,070 --> 00:42:14,400
in international waters.

907
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:16,070
No signal there.

908
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:18,360
No phone service for three days.

909
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:19,630
That gave

910
00:42:19,710 --> 00:42:21,320
Tong Fan and Yinshidai an opportunity.

911
00:42:22,590 --> 00:42:23,360
We need

912
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:26,000
to learn from this.

913
00:42:28,150 --> 00:42:29,000
Fang Wanzhi

914
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:31,030
went rogue and overstepped.

915
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,190
(She should be fired.)

916
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:34,920
It's only natural

917
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:36,920
for newcomers to make mistakes.

918
00:42:37,150 --> 00:42:38,000
Think about yourself.

919
00:42:38,190 --> 00:42:38,670
And me.

920
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,360
Who hasn't made mistakes?

921
00:42:40,670 --> 00:42:42,070
Look at this.

922
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:46,630
She sent this email

923
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,840
three days ago.

924
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:51,190
Her emergency plan
and financial analysis

925
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,670
are pretty good.
